* Dimension\nChanges
** Core Question
***_ What happens when source data changes?
** Three Options
***_ Overwrite (lose history)
***_ Preserve old + create new version
***_ Track limited history (previous column)
** Business Impact
***_ Current state analysis
***_ Historical analysis at time of transaction
***_ Trend analysis over time
** SCD Choice Drives
***_ Table structure complexity
***_ Storage requirements
***_ Query complexity
@endmindmap
